            "title": "海盈山單日沽5伙 高層海景戶呎價達2.73萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"海盈山單日沽5伙，高層海景戶呎價達2.73萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2eba719b598770d581e7507b8bf68377/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031020450868231.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">海盈山單日沽5伙，高層海景戶呎價達2.73萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>嘉里夥拍信和、太古地產及港鐵合作發展的黃竹坑站上蓋港島南岸新盤海盈山，單日沽5伙，套現約6,856.37萬元，成交價由1,077.42萬至1,715.22萬元，其中高層海景2房套單位，成交呎價達27,399元。\n\n</p>\n<p>港島南岸第4期的海盈山分兩期發展，共提供800伙，現時推售的4A期，項目共提供432伙，面積351至1847方呎，涵蓋1房至4房戶型，主打2房戶佔逾60%。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
