        {
            "title": "英超│榜尾3隊歷來最差？ 3隊總分創新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"英超榜尾3隊歷來最差？3隊總分創新低。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9701df6b68a9f8e9fe37b3f5ff27a92c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031019552052770.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">英超榜尾3隊歷來最差？3隊總分創新低。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>李斯特城於周日英超作客0:1不敵車路士，繼續以17分排倒數第2。本輪3支英超升班馬都落敗，各隊的排名和分數不變，繼續排最後3位。而3隊目前合共只有43分，是英超有史以來完成28輪後分數最低的降班區組合。\n\n</p><h2>修咸頓、李斯特城、葉士域治齊輸波</h2>\n<p>修咸頓在本輪作客1:3不敵利物浦，以9分排包尾；李斯特城遠征車路士就輸0:1，繼續以17分居倒數第2；葉士域治造訪水晶宮，亦以相同比數落敗，同樣累積17分列尾3。3隊加起來只有43分，成為英超有史以來完成28輪後同期最差的降班區組合。上季般尼、錫菲聯和盧頓賽完28輪後，合共僅49分，當時已經刷新紀錄，相隔一季又再創歷史新低。值得一提，上季和今季3隊都是升班馬，可見英冠和英超之間的差距。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d450492b3604757d61ae4b1d598d07e/2025-03/1_15.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32ecd68ec4308c2c4d01606abb9c450f/2025-03/2_0_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/255f37e53fdf73d3eb35ce0e800cccec/2025-03/3_14.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f93ed554692a8477ad848d51b56ee8aa/2025-03/4_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李斯特城周日不敵車路士。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a23bba32adaa0fff1bca8cbeb6395508/2025-03/5_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae20d9836d6c94c57b6ea1d523edd838/2025-03/6_11.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/457579e5b990322aa884239076dd25e1/2025-03/7_9.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc0d21993e32266de6f74110e9fb6b9d/2025-03/8_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        修咸頓同樣在本輪輸波，不敵利物浦。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10e90650c989388b936b3af269fa0cfa/2025-03/9_5.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51fba7848bef09e790193651c6a40e01/2025-03/10_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/53086c65b1a654634c54267ba3c58a28/2025-03/11_7.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e231dd8018b5656d8b3b9f8eddac3b05/2025-03/12_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/383ff97b3d4de5638d57f415382b1d83/2025-03/13_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        葉士域治本輪不敵水晶宮。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>3隊合共43分 創英超同期新低</h2>\n<p>同時，自英超成立起，28輪後降班區3隊總分最低的4個球季，全部在近6季內出現，除了上文提到的近2季外，還有2018至19球季的56分，以及2021至22球季的57分，可見近年英超榜尾球隊與中游的距離甚遠。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
