            "title": "安徽85後升格做阿嫲  逆天神顏熱爆網絡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"安徽85後靚嫲嫲餵孫片在網絡熱傳。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a68d344e7afcef843b4c62727f95ddc3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031019550338566.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">安徽85後靚嫲嫲餵孫片在網絡熱傳。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>內地網絡近日廣傳一位85後女子為嬰兒餵奶的影片，該名體態纖瘦，樣貌清麗的女子，原來是嬰兒的嫲嫲，因其逆天顏值，令一眾網民驚嘆，以為她餵養的是其自己的骨肉「說是孩子的媽，我都相信」。\n\n</p><h2>小兒子才5歲</h2>\n<p>據內媒及網上影片顯示，該名僅39歲便榮升做奶奶的女子，是安徽一名服裝店老闆。影片看到，束著馬尾的她，在房間內一邊踱步，一邊為手中約數月大的嬰兒餵奶，手法熟練。片中睡床則躺著一名少婦，相信是嬰兒的母親。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3af38ddfb6d2146e72862cd3a648877e/2025-03/5656_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲熟練地餵孫子。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/21cec53ee2c85de59781396ffdeac4d7/2025-03/5895656.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲熟練地餵孫子。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77e54e1cd2d67e13161994dd1f7b720f/2025-03/78878784_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲熟練地餵孫子。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd7f64d12a82caa0fd04ac99188925d1/2025-03/156456456_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲熟練地餵孫子。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲熟練地餵孫子。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e45621ad7f95423451618eeb4f6b9e9a/2025-03/489485485.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲熟練地餵孫子。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/342b156580e04591772bb36d344bc3e7/2025-03/874784874_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99e4b65683738d317375c721f1e3b3c0/2025-03/45645654663.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神仙嫲嫲的樣貌在網上成為熱話。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"嬰兒的親母在床上休息。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c07a2209f94cb9448f4c124486ea7a2/2025-03/489859859985.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        嬰兒的親母在床上休息。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞:<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-topics/3390921/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E9%AB%98%E6%A0%A1%E7%A5%9E%E4%BB%99%E9%A1%8F%E5%80%BC%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E7%B0%BD%E7%B4%84%E6%88%90%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9B%BE%E5%B0%B1%E7%95%B6%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%89%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6\">河南高校「神仙顏值」女教師簽約成藝人 曾就當小三傳聞報警</a>\n</p>\n<p>拍攝者則說「這是孩子奶奶，要是不知道的，還以為是孩子媽媽呢」。\n\n</p>\n<p>網上消息指，影片中的這名靚嫲嫲，在外地打工賺到第一桶金後，便回鄉開時裝店和成婚，大兒子剛成為父親，小兒子今年才5歲。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞:<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3417276/%E6%9C%80%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%89%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%8790%E5%BE%8C%E5%9F%B7%E6%8E%8C%E5%85%89%E9%9B%BB%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E8%83%8E%E5%95%8A\">最美光二代｜江蘇90後執掌光電巨頭 網民：真會投胎啊</a>\n</p>\n<p>一眾網民，對這位85後嫲嫲的顏值十分欣賞，「可真是逆天了！這保養得也太好了吧」、「80後還有的忙著找對象呢」、「我70後的，孩子還在學校呢」，「都是80後，我還是童子之身，在風中凌亂」，還有不少網友留言開玩笑，「奶奶可以繼續生育」、「奶奶有沒有男朋友？」\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
