        {
            "title": "簡約公屋︱首個項目元朗攸壆路月底入伙  配套設施齊備居民住得安心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"簡約公屋首個項目元朗攸壆路即將入伙  配套設施齊備居民住得安心。短片截圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e15e4babd67927962268005d3e5c83de/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031019425775289.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">簡約公屋首個項目元朗攸壆路即將入伙  配套設施齊備居民住得安心。短片截圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>元朗攸壆路簡約公屋是全港首個簡約公屋項目，該項目將於本月底入伙，項目不僅提供舒適的居住環境，更配備了齊全的配套設施。項目內設有小型超市、便利店及自助洗衣店，滿足居民的日常購物與生活需求。此外，營運機構會提供保安及清潔服務，確保居住環境安全整潔，讓居民住得安心。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129983/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"項目不僅提供舒適的居住環境，更配備了齊全的配套設施。短片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/efee4817b58eb3b79f2e017a1ad07eac/2025-03/125.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        項目不僅提供舒適的居住環境，更配備了齊全的配套設施。短片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129985/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"自助洗衣店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e45e2d89816bd3ed6eb4102514179753/2025-03/126.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        自助洗衣店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129986/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"項目提供康體設施。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c990b2b13626b6c3d6ec098202c53a09/2025-03/127.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        項目提供康體設施。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129987/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"流動中醫車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eee47b43d1483e1337de8a06cb44392a/2025-03/128.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        流動中醫車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129988/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"營運機構會舉辦不同活動，讓項目居民、職員等互動交流。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e35d2aa8ad8f0232ba7b87a7bb14a4e5/2025-03/132_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        營運機構會舉辦不同活動，讓項目居民、職員等互動交流。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>營運機構還為項目提供多元化的服務支援，包括康樂設施及流動中醫車等，讓居民生活更多姿多彩和便利。小朋友和青年還可使用溫習室、活動室，未來營運機構也會舉辦不同活動，讓項目居民、職員等互動交流，建立歸屬感的同時，促進鄰里關係。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
