        {
            "title": "帆船│女子舵手賽維港上演 50位女舵手大鬥法",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"女子舵手賽維港上演，50位女舵手大鬥法。公關圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/41685bed2145477c37ad4968cbb117fd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031019421883908.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">女子舵手賽維港上演，50位女舵手大鬥法。公關圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港遊艇會每年均會舉辦「女子舵手賽」，今年的賽事於周六假維港上演，近50位女舵手及其隊伍共約180位帆手，在維港較勁，並共慶三八國際婦女節。\n\n</p>\n<p>賽事起航綫設於維港東面海域，參賽的女舵手大鬥法，帶領船員競逐多個不同級別或組別帆船的獎項。賽事原本於中午12時30分舉行，可惜一度因為無風而被迫延遲開賽。一小時後，維港海面吹起微風，終可開賽，第二場賽事緊接首場賽事完結結後開始，在和緩的風力下，女帆手們順利完成全日兩場賽事。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「Ffolly 號」在「Flying Fifteen型帆船」組別凱旋。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05431c0a9cefc2ab682952b962c0525c/2025-03/Ffolly_Flying_Fifteen_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「Ffolly 號」在「Flying Fifteen型帆船」組別凱旋。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「Generations 號」船隊榮獲大帆船PHS 組別冠軍。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b7da2b35058d79dd658edff05ba1df4/2025-03/Generations_PHS_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「Generations 號」船隊榮獲大帆船PHS 組別冠軍。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「Impala 1 號」在「Impala型帆船」組別奪冠。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/daed3b912b2d5dd8eb8f8f402931957c/2025-03/Impala_1_Impala_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「Impala 1 號」在「Impala型帆船」組別奪冠。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「Incoming 號」女舵手Jacquie Truhol (左三)帶領船隊在「Etchells型帆船」組別封后。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a967cfe5ba13547dc29103e258f87223/2025-03/Incoming_Jacquie_Truhol_Etchells_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「Incoming 號」女舵手Jacquie Truhol (左三)帶領船隊在「Etchells型帆船」組別封后。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「Victory 9 號」在「Ruffian 型帆船」組別稱后。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/70138194da95efabfff975b2f46b50d3/2025-03/Victory_9_Ruffian_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「Victory 9 號」在「Ruffian 型帆船」組別稱后。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「女子舵手賽」周六於維港上演。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b60c04b8f5909ebdc5dfd861f9cbc110/2025-03/174160659292250.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「女子舵手賽」周六於維港上演。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Etchells型帆船女將田妙韻(右一)已是第三度挑戰「女子舵手賽」，是次賽事更是全女班上陣。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1014e088d097d7ec51f8858530b8f25f/2025-03/Etchells_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Etchells型帆船女將田妙韻(右一)已是第三度挑戰「女子舵手賽」，是次賽事更是全女班上陣。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"女將楊姿詠(左二)表示，期望見到更多女性加入帆船運動，畢竟女性心思較為細密，對陣上決策較為有利。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/adcf1d7d0887e37e18a8c0e9a8f91a70/2025-03/174160659330908.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女將楊姿詠(左二)表示，期望見到更多女性加入帆船運動，畢竟女性心思較為細密，對陣上決策較為有利。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"李加恩(左)首次參加女子舵手賽，初出即為其船隊「Panache 號」榮登「Pandora 型帆船」的冠軍寶座。公關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62b28ff523b07fb1877166559d37daa4/2025-03/Panache_Pandora_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        李加恩(左)首次參加女子舵手賽，初出即為其船隊「Panache 號」榮登「Pandora 型帆船」的冠軍寶座。公關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>「Generations 號」贏得大帆船PHS 組別；「Incoming 號」和「Ffolly 號」分別在Etchells型帆船Flying Fifteen 型帆船及奪冠。各位業餘女帆船運動員都努力比賽，當中在「Etchells型帆船」比賽的田妙韻，已是第三度挑戰「女子舵手賽」，今次上陣的船員更是「全女將」，實屬難得。另外，女將楊姿詠表示，期望見到更多女性加入帆船運動，畢竟女性心思較為細密，對陣上決策較為有利。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
